    "created_at": "2012-05-26T17:15:15Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-05-26T17:15:15Z",
    "body": "Hex `1c0` is octal `700` (decimal `448`), which sets the permission to `rwx------`.\n\nWe may just want to set it to `rwxrwxrwx` (octal `777`, decimal `484`) and let the system default reduce that to whatever it wants, e.g., `rwxrw-rw-`, but I'm not entirely sure if it would bitwise and with the default like I expect, or just overwrite it.\n",
